resource_title: TED: Heather Brooke: My Battle to expose government corruption.
long_description: Our leaders need to be held accountable, says journalist Heather Brooke. And she should know: Brooke uncovered the British Parliamentary financial expenses that led to a major political scandal in 2009. She urges us to ask our leaders questions through platforms like Freedom of Information requests -- and to finally get some answers.
learning_objective: To find out if the bulk import tool works.
